cs.LG, cs.RO, cs.AI, cs.SY, cs.CV 

The paper involves machine learning, control theory, and computer vision, which are all relevant to the sub-categories of cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.RO (Robotics), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.SY (Systems and Control), and cs.CV (Computer Vision). The focus on predicting human behavior and collision avoidance also suggests cs.LG and cs.AI as the most likely sub-categories.
